      <h4><b>Milky Mushroom Soup</b></h4>
      
      <div class="text-left">
<p class="title"><b>INGREDIENTS:</b></p>
   <p>
      <li>1 Pack (400 gr) mushrooms</li>
      <li>1 Tbsp butter</li>
      <li>1 Tbsp olive oil</li>
      <li>3 Tbsp flour</li>
      <li>1 Cup milk</li>
      <li>4 Cups water</li>
      <li>Black pepper</li>
      <li>Salt</li>
  </p>
