      <p class="title"><b>PREPARATION:</b></p>
      <li><b>1.</b> Mix olive oil and butter in a pot.</li>
      <li><b>2.</b> Add the flour and fry.</li>
      <li><b>3.</b> Add 1 cup of milk slowly and stir constantly.</li>
      <li><b>4.</b> Add chopped mushrooms, water, salt, pepper and cook it until boiled.</li>
      <li><b>5.</b> After the soup has boiled, turn the fire down and wait another 5 minutes then serve.</li>
